categories: Category:Military officers of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Keeling was a male Human officer of the reconstituted Sith Empire during the Cold War. In 3643 BBY he was stationed on Nar Shaddaa, where after recovering stolen intelligence reports with Republic Strategic Information Service slicing signatures, he send an Imperial to destroy the Republic listening post, from which Imperial communications were intercepted.
Officer Keeling appears in the Star Wars: The Old Republic as an NPC on Nar Shaddaa and starts the mission "The Walls Have Ears."
